title: Virginia State Forest Property Boundaries
name: Virginia State Forest Property Boundaries
description: This dataset contains 1:24000-scale State Forest property boundary polygons for the State of Virginia. In this case, State Forests are defined as forest properties owned and/or managed by the Virginia Department of Forestry. For example, two of the properties in this dataset are owned by the Virginia Department of Conservation and Recreation, but are managed by the Virginia Department of Forestry and so are included. Property boundaries were derived using several methods and varying bases data sources.
